      "content": "\"own my narrative\"? how am i supposed to do that when they've already decided who i am? there's no winning. even if i face it, they'll just find something else to tear me apart. it's just exhausting. i'm just so incredibly lonely and it feels like the only way to actually get some peace and quiet from all of this is to just... not be here anymore. like, just disappear so the noise finally stops.",
